OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773929472
OL,3,CProbable case of meningococcal
OL,4,Cinvestigated at NI school
OL,6,FHealth officials in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fare investigating a probable case of
OL,8,Fmeningococcal disease in a pupil at a
OL,9,FBelfast school.
OL,11,FThe Public Health Agency (PHA) said
OL,12,Fthe case is not linked to the ongoing
OL,13,Fmeningitis outbreak in England, which
OL,14,Fhas claimed the lives of two young
OL,15,Fpeople.
OL,17,FParents of children at Bloomfield
OL,18,FCollegiate School in the east of the
OL,19,Fcity have been contacted by health
OL,20,Fofficials.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
