FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773929472
OL,3,CProbable case of meningococcal
OL,4,Cinvestigated at NI school
OL,6,FThe PHA said: "The Public Health
OL,7,FAgency is aware of a probable case of
OL,8,Fmeningococcal disease in a 16yearold
OL,9,Fpupil who attends a secondary school
OL,10,Fin Belfast.
OL,12,F"All appropriate public health actions
OL,13,Fhave now been completed.
OL,15,F"As a precaution, PHA has been working
OL,16,Fclosely with the school and has issued
OL,17,Finformation to parents and guardians.
OL,19,F"Relevant guidance has also been
OL,20,Fshared with GP out-of-hours services
OL,21,Fand emergency departments.
OL,26,@nD@OOUtD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773929472
OL,3,CProbable case of meningococcal
OL,4,Cinvestigated at NI school
OL,6,F"We urge students, staff and families
OL,7,Fto remain vigilant for the signs and
OL,8,Fsymptoms of meningitis and act fast if
OL,9,Fthey suspect they may have it."
OL,11,FMeningococcal disease can cause
OL,12,Fmeningitis.
OL,14,FThe PHA said it would continue to
OL,15,Fmonitor the situation.
OL,17,FThe statement added "PHA is aware of
OL,18,Fthe meningitis incident in Kent and is
OL,19,Fparticipating in regular UK-wide
OL,20,Fmeetings in relation to this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]yD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773929472
OL,3,CProbable case of meningococcal
OL,4,Cinvestigated at NI school
OL,6,F"To date there is no evidence of
OL,7,Fspread beyond the south east of
OL,8,FEngland."
OL,10,FPhilip McGuigan, the chairman of
OL,11,FStormont's Health Committee, said he
OL,12,Fwould write to Health Minister Mike
OL,13,FNesbitt to ask what action he was
OL,14,Ftaking.
OL,16,FMr McGuigan said: "This will be a
OL,17,Fdeeply worrying time for many
OL,18,Ffollowing the deaths of two young
OL,19,Fpeople in Britain and the increased
OL,20,Fnumber of cases following the outbreak.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]xD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
