OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1773929472
OL,3,CProbable case of meningococcal
OL,4,Cinvestigated at NI school
OL,6,F"What we need to see now is clear and
OL,7,Furgent direction from the minister to
OL,8,Freassure the public that there will be
OL,9,Fplans in place in the event that the
OL,10,Fdisease spreads.
OL,12,F"I would urge anyone who thinks they
OL,13,Fmay have symptoms to seek medical
OL,14,Fadvice immediately."
